comment: The law is the law. Just because your at best a b list celebrity doesn't mean the law doesn't apply to you.
commentable_entity.ask: Amber Heard should face charges of perjury for lying under oath.
commentable_entity.title: Amber Heard should face charges of perjury for lying under oath.
commentable_entity.description:
It has become apparent, from watching the Johnny Depp vs Amber Heard defamation court case, that there are serious questions that need answering around Heard’s previous testimony.

Amber Heard stated, under oath, during the libel court case (Johnny Depp vs The Sun Newspaper) that she donated her entire divorce settlement to charity. This was a blatant lie that was exposed during the defamation court proceedings. As such, I feel that in the name of justice, she should face perjury charges for lying under oath
